--- Thread (10 messages, 2021-06-18) ---
[2021-06-18 10:41] velizar_ (Name): The bot clicks ebb to buy drones
[2021-06-18 10:42] velizar_ (Name): This is probably good because buying drones in the lategame is generally bad
[2021-06-18 10:42] velizar_ (Name): And the bot keeps buying drones way after it shouldn't
[2021-06-18 10:43] velizar_ (Name): So this usage of ebb removes a bad choice
[2021-06-18 10:43] velizar_ (Name): Now I wonder whether the following is a viable strategy:
[2021-06-18 10:45] velizar_ (Name): Buy a bunch of ebbs;
Buy some conduits and just enough trinitys or dynamos that you can turn the green into gold;
Have with breach-proof green extra set attackers;
[2021-06-18 10:45] velizar_ (Name): Initially use the conduits for gold;
[2021-06-18 10:46] velizar_ (Name): But there's always the threat that you're going to click all of your ebbs, and use the green to buy a lot of attackers
[2021-06-18 10:46] velizar_ (Name): Eventually really do that.
[2021-06-18 10:46] velizar_ (Name): Now you're breach-proof too

